{"tid":1943204,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★環翠邨財困夫妻燒炭亡","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T06:51:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":128,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"5d317188a6e330dd9d8db26136b09076a419b8ba","tid":1943204,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"據悉，男死者姓何(47歲)，任職珠寶店，女死者姓曾(52歲)，化妝品店職員。兩夫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>妻因金錢問題尋死</strong></span>，並用膠紙密封門窗後燒炭。案發單位面積約300呎，放有一張床，現場沒有打鬥痕迹，警方檢獲遺書，內容透露因財困輕生，同時向家人交代身後事。警方經初步調查，不排除兩夫妻燒炭時曾經飲酒，案件列作自殺協定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/bkn-20200325185249986-0325_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200325%2Fbkn-20200325185249986-0325_00822_001.html&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=86698ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/bkn-20200325185249986-0325_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9d9c91d17d14723da9720708d665b812597c620d","tid":1943204,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac279078d5ba0bd93b27ab662390199b39332a2","tid":1943204,"uid":295650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d9c91d17d14723da9720708d665b812597c620d","tid":1943204,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" c